title: Merlin  (2003) ( Dragonz) cbr
description:
Slowly, the old Celtic tradition linked to the gods goes away ... The people forget about it and now go to the One God. But that's not counting the goddess Ahes!
Aided by her most trusted elves, she devises a plan to regain the esteem of her former followers, creating a savior entirely devoted to the ancient tradition.
She then orders Elaum, a spirit of air, to bind with a virgin ... But wil her plans will take place as she has planned?

enjoy
